data.description: Excellent investor opportunity for a rare furnished and fully leased quadraplex ideally located in an X-Flood zone. The property has undergone multiple upgrades including a new roof (2021) A/C, plumbing, and electrical upgrades, all-tile, side-by-side washer/dryer hook-ups in every unit, and so much more!  Attached to the property is an additional lot that can be separated or build additional properties to add to your portfolio.  All tenants work and will need at least 24 hours notice to show.  Depending on tenant schedules, we may not be able to show all units at the same time. City Utilities in an paid.
